lead_paragraph: Lamar Jackson of Louisville and Baker Mayfield of Oklahoma were named finalists for the both the Maxwell player of the award and the Davey O'Brien Award that goes to the best quarterback in college football.

headline.print_headline: Jackson, Mayfield, Peppers Up for Two College Football Award
